name: Arkanoid: The Lost Levels
overview: Arkanoid - The Lost Levels Compact 1, based on the ROM for Arkanoid: Doh it Again, combines the original Arkanoid, Tournament Arkanoid and some of Amiga Alternate Levels into 1. The reason why it’s called “Compact” is because Arkanoid Doh it Again only has room for 10 blocks by 16, whereas the others are 11-13 horizontally and more than 16 vertically.
